gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 125, Hawks 117
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Hawks, 125-117, as they improved to 39-12 on the season. Kristaps Porzingis led the Celtics with 31 points (13-19 FG) as Derrick White (21 points, five 3PT, six rebounds, seven assists) and Jayson Tatum (20 points, nine rebounds, seven assists) totaled 41 points. Saddiq Bey led Atlanta with 25 points as Trae Young tallied 20 points and 10 assists in the loss. The Hawks moved to 22-29 on the season.
